ote><br />\n一個幾月 係咪要堅持耐啲<br />\n而加一個月 對於男仔追女黎講都叫耐啦</blockquote><br />\n我都keep左幾個月<br />\n平均2~3日就揾個女仔<br />\n每次可以由佢放intern傾到訓<br />\n但我成日都心入面計佢揾左我幾多次<br />\n3次呀<br />\n究竟你想點呀<br />\n我特登停左唔揾佢有一星期<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n你有無搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c676153bcff5bd535b707eaea15c926cd7c316","tid":400390,"uid":117267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfccdc7eef4f9c2b1449369b2a997147884ecf27","tid":400390,"uid":37857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:34:47.000Z","msg":"我明😢"},{"pid":"14efa93834dbc201e89df68f69d5155d9aac53c6","tid":400390,"uid":78619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名睇人話你唔識做主動</blockquote><br />\n主動太耐去認識一個男仔 我攰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾耐</blockquote><br />\n一個幾月 係咪要堅持耐啲<br />\n而加一個月 對於男仔追女黎講都叫耐啦</blockquote><br />\n我都keep左幾個月<br />\n平均2~3日就揾個女仔<br />\n每次可以由佢放intern傾到訓<br />\n但我成日都心入面計佢揾左我幾多次<br />\n3次呀<br />\n究竟你想點呀<br />\n我特登停左唔揾佢有一星期<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n你有無搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過隔一個月<br />\n之後傾左幾日<br />\n最後都放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係無得勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24df37c7c3c4997fdb0706b62413f20f3989258","tid":400390,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:35:20.000Z","msg":"算啦 <br />\n好快你就會明 唔係你嘅就點都唔係你嘅<br />\n然後你就會覺得自己當時點解咁蠢仲比希望自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}